title: tour post !!
body:
quick note: contemplated for quite some time on whether should I post a photo of me bc I’m insecure af and I don’t really like having photos of me taken so… but I decided to just do it. so here’s a rare one of my sis and I 🙈 (idk if my sister wants the internet to know her, hence the emoji)

@taylorswift hey T! my name’s Jen from Malaysia. so I’m not gonna say much here bc I already made a longer one on my main acc @stellaireskies ☺️

Taylor, I don’t think I’ll ever be able to put my love for you into words. you’re just such a warm-hearted and precious person like I’ll never get how anyone can not like you?? you make me want to be the best version of myself and I thank you for that. I also thank you for your words, whether in the form of lyrics or speeches or poems, for they hold such invaluable wisdom and have helped me through some rough times. you’ve helped me grow, no actually, we have both grown so thank you for growing with me. it fills my heart with joy to see that you’re at such a good place right now.

I’m so proud of how far you’ve come and I’ll stand by you, always.

so I’ll be seeing you at the Tokyo night 1 show on the 20th of November… which is a day after my birthday, just so you know ;)

I can’t wait to have the best time and I hope I’ll be able to give you a hug too! @taylorswift I love you ❤️

p.s. PLEASE SING COME BACK BE HERE AGAIN OR BACK TO DECEMBER OR SAFE AND SOUND THANKS X
